{"tid":195129,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彩虹站都市傳說原來係真！","createTime":"2017-04-10T11:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T12:55:38.000Z","uid":99828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"489850379a0995855d9ea6fd0d5d1b16c8e4243d","tid":195129,"uid":99828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:58:18.000Z","msg":"彩虹站神秘路軌通向&hellip; 港鐵鬧鬼傳說大揭秘<br />\n<br />\n傳說一：遲遲未到站<br />\n<br />\n有傳 34 年前，彩虹站通車，幾名英國工程師和本地的車務人員登上第一列電動列車試車。本應短餖四分鐘的車程，下一站卻遲遲未見，途中又遇上了無線電系統失靈，致電車長卻只聽到「沙沙」聲。等了十多分鐘，列車終於到站，但所有乘客都面色蒼白、受驚過度而不能言語。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.e-zone.com.hk/channelnews.php?id=19513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.e-zone.com.hk%2Fchannelnews.php%3Fid%3D19513&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=c36f36b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.e-zone.com.hk/channelnews.php?id=19513</a><br />\n<br />\n被破解<br />\n<br />\n港鐵大癱瘓  列車停管道 逾百乘客摸黑行路軌疏散<br />\n<br />\n港鐵放工時間出現大故障，觀塘綫九龍灣站附近的架空電纜出現故障，觀塘站至九龍灣站列車癱瘓。事發時，其中一部列車正由彩虹駛往鑽石山，途中因電力中斷停在路軌，車廂的冷氣停止運作，車長打開車門疏散乘客，逾百乘客落路軌，沿管道徒步前往鑽石山站月台，其間管道內的照明系統仍正常。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170410/large/1491823062_3581.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170410%2Flarge%2F1491823062_3581.jpg&h=e1c6bd54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170410/56547429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170410%2F56547429&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtJzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=a5a5afc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170410%2F56547429&h=bc3ee861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170410/56547429</a>"},{"pid":"3aefc1d74942510e89cbc48e55d1a9e31873a46c","tid":195129,"uid":99828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T11:58:51.000Z","msg":"已經唔係傳說"},{"pid":"1b43fa659cbd60d4f53e99007996dbb0906c3565","tid":195129,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:01:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f1c24856d6f72eb12dc676b63d5d60b5b1091d4","tid":195129,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:03:20.000Z","msg":"我都試過 架列車係彩虹個陣入左另一條路軌 跟住 故障5-10分鐘"},{"pid":"99295b8560cadfe670f0b98da7fd876bf357dbf0","tid":195129,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba32c46c4c042bc8f2c707b7902ca5de152a3bdd","tid":195129,"uid":25194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都試過 架列車係彩虹個陣入左另一條路軌 跟住 故障5-10分鐘</blockquote><br />\n屌 前幾日咪咁"},{"pid":"0581733fd5ac3ab1167fd326311b8f158aabf760","tid":195129,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:34:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>被破解<br />\n<br />\n港鐵大癱瘓  列車停管道 逾百乘客摸黑行路軌疏散</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇到呢度笑"},{"pid":"06e398d26c6eb0df6a19787a5eba11f9af01b20a","tid":195129,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:36:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>被破解<br />\n<br />\n港鐵大癱瘓  列車停管道 逾百乘客摸黑行路軌疏散</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇到呢度笑</blockquote><br />\n再睇落去又唔好笑，<br />\n應該根據上邊件事再作落去好笑d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc83ba04cfe67f42ae9e28ea70edda5c94aeb063","tid":195129,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/